have not been confirmed yet.

8
00:02:22,020 --> 00:02:22,940
If you have any ideas,

9
00:02:23,029 --> 00:02:24,520
feel free to tell me anytime.

10
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:25,920
Of course,

11
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:27,560
throughout the recording process,

12
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:29,740
