00:36:59,540 --> 00:37:00,610
Thank you.

547
00:37:01,570 --> 00:37:02,450
I'll be right back.

548
00:37:19,410 --> 00:37:20,910
Seeing a psychiatrist

549
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:22,340
is not a big deal.

550
00:37:22,620 --> 00:37:24,840
It's just like talking
to a hole in a tree.

551
00:37:26,060 --> 00:37:26,990
Let me tell you this.

552
00:37:27,070 --> 00:37:28,060
Human brains are

553
00:37:28,150 --> 00:37:30,140
just like a container

554
00:37:30,230 --> 00:37:32,020
filled with different emotions.

555
00:37:32,110 --> 00:37:34,370
Sometimes, you'll have to empty it out.

556
00:37:34,520 --> 00:37:36,230
If you don't,

557
00:37:38,140 --> 00:37:39,970
it will explode.

558
00:37:42,860 --> 00:37:43,740
I'm getting off now.

559
00:37:48,050 --> 00:37:49,710
Liang Mu Ze,
you must attend the appointment.

560
00:37:49,890 --> 00:37:50,870
You must.

561
00:37:53,590 --> 00:37:55,090
You really must.

562
00:38:00,230 --> 00:38:01,890
Make way please.

563
00:38:02,370 --> 00:38:03,430
Xia Chu?

564
00:38:04,080 --> 00:38:04,870
Xia Chu.

565
00:38:05,100 --> 00:38:05,980
Mi Gu.

566
00:38:06,190 --> 00:38:07,450
-Xia Chu.
-Mi Gu.

567
00:38:08,210 --> 00:38:09,190
Xia Chu.

568
00:38:09,300 --> 00:38:10,400
Mi...

569
00:38:15,630 --> 00:38:17,250
-Zhuo Ran is in the emergency room.
-What?

570
00:38:17,340 --> 00:38:18,880
Zhuo Ran is in the emergency room.

571
00:38:35,380 --> 00:38:38,040
The radiograph of your left ventricle
and coronary artery

572
00:38:38,240 --> 00:38:39,300
shows no sign of infarction.

573
00:38:39,430 --> 00:38:41,450
We can eliminate the possibility of
myocardial infarction.

574
00:38:41,540 --> 00:38:43,050
However, we've found that

575
00:38:43,450 --> 00:38:46,790
at the apex of your heart,
most of the ventricles don't contract.

576
00:38:46,920 --> 00:38:50,140
From the radiography, a swollen ventricle
that looked like a wilting octopus is seen

577
00:38:50,300 --> 00:38:52,840
and the markers of myocardial damage

578
00:38:53,270 --> 00:38:54,570
has started to increase.

579
00:38:55,240 --> 00:38:56,340
It means

580
00:38:57,520 --> 00:38:58,750
death of heart muscles.

581
00:39:00,070 --> 00:39:01,450
Judging by your current condition,

582
00:39:01,550 --> 00:39:04,010
I can say that the dizziness

583
00:39:04,230 --> 00:39:06,170
and chest-pain is all due to

584
00:39:06,710 --> 00:39:08,700
stress cardiomyopathy.

585
00:39:08,790 --> 00:39:10,100
Stress cardiomyopathy?

586
00:39:12,680 --> 00:39:13,930
You've always been healthy.

587
00:39:14,020 --> 00:39:15,340
You even wanted to
get into a military school.

588
00:39:15,430 --> 00:39:16,970
How can you have stress cardiomyopathy?

589
00:39:19,860 --> 00:39:20,740
Xia Chu.

590
00:39:22,770 --> 00:39:24,020
This condition

591
00:39:24,200 --> 00:39:25,280
is usually caused by

592
00:39:25,360 --> 00:39:27,720
intense emotional or physical stress.

593
00:39:27,810 --> 00:39:28,860
For example,

594
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:30,230
a shock,

595
00:39:30,910 --> 00:39:31,690
deep fear

596
00:39:31,790 --> 00:39:33,970
or a sudden loss of a loved one

597
00:39:34,250 --> 00:39:35,590
which can cause an epilepsy attack.

598
00:39:37,870 --> 00:39:39,650
In your case, it's because
of a phone call.

599
00:39:44,780 --> 00:39:46,080
I want to talk to Xia Chu

600
00:39:46,450 --> 00:39:47,470
in private.

601
00:39:48,560 --> 00:39:49,740
No problem.

602
00:39:51,800 --> 00:39:52,900
Don't get worked up.

603
00:39:55,430 --> 00:39:56,190
Do your ward rounds

604
00:39:56,270 --> 00:39:57,890
-20 minutes later.
-Yes.

605
00:40:05,940 --> 00:40:06,970
Liang Mu Ze.

606
00:40:08,790 --> 00:40:09,770
Why are you here?

607
00:40:09,960 --> 00:40:11,010
I'm looking for someone.

608
00:40:11,100 --> 00:40:11,940
Is it Zhuo Ran?

609
00:40:12,030 --> 00:40:12,930
No, Xia Chu.

610
00:40:13,740 --> 00:40:15,600
Why is everyone asking for her today?

611
00:40:15,890 --> 00:40:17,320
-Who else did?
-Director Zhang.

612
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:18,970
I just got a call
from Cardio Surgery Department.

613
00:40:19,060 --> 00:40:20,900
They need you to check on ward 18.

614
00:40:20,990 --> 00:40:21,510
Alright, I got it.

615
00:40:21,590 --> 00:40:22,730
I'll get back to work now.

616
00:40:25,660 --> 00:40:26,690
She is in that ward.

617
00:40:26,820 --> 00:40:27,720
Go on.

618
00:40:38,670 --> 00:40:39,930
I met Mi Gu just now.

619
00:40:40,090 --> 00:40:41,580
She told me you're in the hospital.

620
00:40:44,500 --> 00:40:45,760
She sent you here?

621
00:40:46,240 --> 00:40:47,750
You were together last night?

622
00:40:48,530 --> 00:40:50,830
What's with the phone call?

623
00:40:57,660 --> 00:40:59,280
You have to tell me, Zhuo Ran.

624
00:40:59,620 --> 00:41:00,800
What did you call me just now?

625
00:41:01,080 --> 00:41:02,060
Zhuo Ran.

626
00:41:02,370 --> 00:41:03,700
You still remember this person,

627
00:41:04,560 --> 00:41:05,440
don't you?

628
00:41:10,260 --> 00:41:11,360
Of course I do.

629
00:41:14,300 --> 00:41:15,490
What are you saying?

630
00:41:16,670 --> 00:41:17,650
You do remember.

631
00:41:18,250 --> 00:41:19,230
You should also remember

632
00:41:20,460 --> 00:41:22,850
those weekends you spent together,

633
00:41:23,620 --> 00:41:25,480
those detective novels you read together,

634
00:41:26,200 --> 00:41:27,650
the path you took together after school,

635
00:41:28,790 --> 00:41:30,010
that bottle of water,

636
00:41:30,670 --> 00:41:31,730
that diary

637
00:41:32,150 --> 00:41:33,650
and the never-ending letters
you wrote each other.

638
00:41:33,790 --> 00:41:34,810
All those memories

639
00:41:35,060 --> 00:41:36,800
were your past with Zhuo Ran.

640
00:41:37,000 --> 00:41:37,880
It's Zhuo Ran.

641
00:41:38,030 --> 00:41:39,210
Xia Chu, it's Zhuo Ran.

642
00:41:39,470 --> 00:41:40,350
It's Zhuo Ran.

643
00:41:40,930 --> 00:41:41,850
Calm down, Zhuo Ran.

644
00:41:41,950 --> 00:41:42,970
-You can't get up...
-This.

645
00:41:43,980 --> 00:41:44,860
This part of me

646
00:41:44,960 --> 00:41:45,840
almost stopped beating

647
00:41:46,430 --> 00:41:48,220
just now.

648
00:41:48,430 --> 00:41:49,330
It's because

649
00:41:51,030 --> 00:41:52,060
I was sad

650
00:41:52,460 --> 00:41:54,160
that you forgot Zhuo Ran.

651
00:42:02,790 --> 00:42:05,060
I need to do my ward rounds now.
I'll visit you later.

652
00:42:05,940 --> 00:42:07,160
That comrade...

653
00:42:13,030 --> 00:42:14,370
Don't be with him.

654
00:42:19,270 --> 00:42:20,780
Are you kidding me?

655
00:42:21,350 --> 00:42:22,810
It can't be him.

656
00:42:31,350 --> 00:42:33,080
Anyone can misunderstand
my relationship with him,

657
00:42:34,060 --> 00:42:35,370
but not you.

658
00:42:36,620 --> 00:42:38,160
For a very long time,

659
00:42:38,360 --> 00:42:39,690
I can't even stand
hearing the words,

660
00:42:39,790 --> 00:42:40,810
special force.

661
00:42:41,270 --> 00:42:42,520
Let alone getting into a relationship.

662
00:42:45,350 --> 00:42:46,840
You should know the reason.

663
00:43:01,240 --> 00:43:02,300
Xia Chu.

664
00:43:03,690 --> 00:43:04,710
Why are you here?

665
00:43:08,920 --> 00:43:10,100
It was in the car?

666
00:43:10,940 --> 00:43:12,040
I'm so forgetful.

667
00:43:12,230 --> 00:43:13,730
Sorry for causing you trouble.

668
00:43:14,130 --> 00:43:15,190
Thank you.

669
00:43:17,800 --> 00:43:19,030
Where are you going?

670
00:43:19,120 --> 00:43:19,910
I'm going to visit Xiao Jun.

671
00:43:20,000 --> 00:43:21,490
Have you seen the psychiatrist?

672
00:43:22,910 --> 00:43:24,210
I am talking to you.

673
00:43:24,720 --> 00:43:26,180
-No, I didn't.
-Why?

674
00:43:26,510 --> 00:43:27,530
I don't want to.

675
00:43:28,400 --> 00:43:30,410
Liang Mu Ze,
do you still want the photo?

676
00:43:31,980 --> 00:43:32,970
It's up to you.

677
00:43:49,710 --> 00:43:50,880
<i>Where are you?</i>

